summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Department of Lighting; authorizing an agreement with Walter M. Hupp and Gaile B. Hupp, his wife, William H. Simmons and Susan S. Simmons, and Bertha R. Simmons granting permission to maintain an encroachment (portion of building) into transmission line easement right-of-way in a portion the southwest quarter of the northeast quarter of Section 9, Township 26 North, Range 5 East, W.M.
